Dialogue: 2,0:22:12.72,0:22:14.93,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,決定返回之後兩天
Dialogue: 2,0:22:16.31,0:22:17.68,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,走進死路了
Dialogue: 2,0:22:17.98,0:22:19.44,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,又是死路
Dialogue: 2,0:22:21.31,0:22:22.77,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 2,0:22:23.02,0:22:24.02,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好睏
Dialogue: 2,0:22:24.48,0:22:25.57,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,喉嚨好乾
Dialogue: 2,0:22:26.15,0:22:28.86,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,找不到路 就快要死了
