Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:26.85,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,稀奇的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:30.47,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,拼命迎難而上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.47,0:00:31.93,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,「4」實現著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:33.34,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,時而夢想如願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:37.14,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,吃個飯一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:40.24,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,帶著火 走著海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:43.65,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,向天空進發 於地底探索
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:46.90,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,即便羞愧不會後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:49.65,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,這愛也值得稱讚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.12,0:00:53.32,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,命運
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:56.36,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,一直許願 一直許願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:58.45,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,僅僅是祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:01:01.42,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,即便雷聲震耳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:04.34,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,錯誤也成為幽默
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:06.54,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,No Way
