Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:11.63,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,一邊遮住眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.63,0:01:14.69,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,大家聯結的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.69,0:01:17.77,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,最美好的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:21.56,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,禮物般的奇緣
